{"word":"πίπτω","slug":"πίπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πίπτω</el></b> [‘fall’, the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> of the idea conveyed in <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάλλω\">βάλλω</a></el>] ‘drop from a relatively high position to a lower’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> fall <a href='B:470 10:29'>Mt 10:29</a>; <a href='B:470 13:4'>13:4f</a>; <a href='B:470 15:27'>15:27</a>; <a href='B:470 17:15'>17:15</a>; <a href='B:470 24:29'>24:29</a>; <a href='B:490 10:18'>Lk 10:18</a>; <a href='B:510 5:5'>Ac 5:5</a>; <a href='B:510 9:4'>9:4</a>; <a href='B:510 20:9'>20:9</a>; <a href='B:730 6:13'>Rv 6:13</a>; <a href='B:730 9:1'>9:1</a>;collapse <a href='B:470 7:25'>Mt 7:25</a>; <a href='B:490 13:4'>Lk 13:4</a>; <a href='B:650 11:30'>Hb 11:30</a>.</b> In imagery <b>fall <a href='B:490 11:17'>Lk 11:17</a>; <a href='B:510 1:26'>Ac 1:26</a>; <a href='B:510 13:11'>13:11</a>; <a href='B:730 7:16'>Rv 7:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> fall (down)</b> in worshipful or petitioning gesture <b><a href='B:470 2:11'>Mt 2:11</a>; <a href='B:470 4:9'>4:9</a>; <a href='B:470 17:6'>17:6</a>; <a href='B:470 26:39'>26:39</a>; <a href='B:480 5:22'>Mk 5:22</a>; <a href='B:500 11:32'>J 11:32</a>; <a href='B:730 4:10'>Rv 4:10</a>; <a href='B:730 22:8'>22:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> by <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of the idea in a, experience disaster<b>fall/perish <a href='B:490 21:24'>Lk 21:24</a>; <a href='B:530 10:8'>1 Cor 10:8</a>; <a href='B:650 3:17'>Hb 3:17</a>; <a href='B:660 5:12'>Js 5:12</a>; <a href='B:730 2:5'>Rv 2:5</a>; <a href='B:730 11:13'>11:13</a>; <a href='B:730 14:8'>14:8</a>;</b> in related manner<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>d.</pp></b> of moral or spiritual failure <b>fall <a href='B:520 11:11'>Ro 11:11</a>, <a href='B:520 11:22'>22</a>; <a href='B:520 14:4'>14:4</a>; <a href='B:530 10:12'>1 Cor 10:12</a>; <a href='B:530 13:8'>13:8</a>; <a href='B:650 4:11'>Hb 4:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bo